完整执行以下所有步骤，不要遗漏任何细节。&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="一创建目录结构">一、创建目录结构&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>创建以下目录：&lt;br>
raw/articles/&lt;br>
raw/clippings/&lt;br>
raw/images/&lt;br>
raw/pdfs/&lt;br>
raw/notes/&lt;br>
raw/personal/&lt;br>
wiki/sources/&lt;br>
wiki/concepts/&lt;br>
wiki/entities/&lt;br>
wiki/synthesis/&lt;br>
wiki/templates/&lt;br>
outputs/&lt;br>
scripts/&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="二创建系统文件">二、创建系统文件&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 id="wikiindexmd">wiki/index.md&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>frontmatter 包含：type: system-index, graph-excluded: true&lt;br>
正文包含：Sources 列表（按日期倒序）、Concepts 列表、Entities 列表、Recent Synthesis 列表、Outputs 列表&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>cursor</title><link>https://bluespace.eu.org/post/%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7/%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5/cursor/</link><pubDate>Fri, 27 Mar 2026 14:54:21 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://bluespace.eu.org/post/%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7/%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5/cursor/</guid><description>&lt;p>下载&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://cursor.com/cn">Cursor: The best way to code with AI&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>安装&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="images/7ee6d65b-0220-480d-86b1-34efcce6b8c8.png" alt="image.png">&lt;img src="images/6146fce6-30c0-4bc5-9a16-89d42769bb7f.png" alt="image.png">&lt;img src="images/9a37842a-0ac5-42d4-ab28-4bbe8a950430.png" alt="image.png">选择loginin,使用账号&lt;a href="mailto:user@example.com">user@example.com&lt;/a> 选择邮箱验证码登陆（验证码找**）。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="images/176f6039-ca70-4692-8132-df208c391508.png" alt="image.png">使用&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="images/468c60f9-9240-4c6f-9666-da3feac426ed.png" alt="image.png">&lt;img src="images/5afe4587-1c1d-4da1-88ab-302fa695b632.png" alt="image.png">然后就可以对话的方式编写项目代码了。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>一共有4种模式&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="images/894cecf4-8175-4bf3-afc7-6f2d93e48373.png" alt="image.png">1.建议在开始编码之前先使用“plan”模式进入规划，该阶段主要是澄清需求和编码设计。这个阶段非常重要不建议省略，因为前期描述清楚需求做好规划设计能有效减少返工。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>2.在规划完成后，选择“agent”模式进入编码模式，开始正式编码。这个时候会开始自主编码，可能会涉及并增删改文件，建议提取做好git备份，方便随时回滚。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Shadowsocks内网穿透配置</title><link>https://bluespace.eu.org/post/%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7/shadowsocks%E5%86%85%E7%BD%91%E7%A9%BF%E9%80%8F%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/</link><pubDate>Sat, 28 Feb 2026 13:33:41 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://bluespace.eu.org/post/%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7/shadowsocks%E5%86%85%E7%BD%91%E7%A9%BF%E9%80%8F%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="shadowsocks-内网穿透配置">Shadowsocks 内网穿透配置&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="服务端配置">服务端配置&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 id="1-安装-shadowsocks-服务端">1. 安装 Shadowsocks 服务端&lt;/h3>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1"># Ubuntu/Debian&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">apt install shadowsocks-libev
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1"># 启动服务&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">systemctl start shadowsocks-libev
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">systemctl &lt;span class="nb">enable&lt;/span> shadowsocks-libev
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="2-配置服务端">2. 配置服务端&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>编辑配置文件 &lt;code>/etc/shadowsocks-libev/config.json&lt;/code>：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-json" data-lang="json">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;server&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;xxx.xxx.xxx.xxx&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;server_port&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mi">8388&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;password&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;&amp;lt;密码&amp;gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;timeout&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mi">300&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;method&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;aes-256-gcm&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="3-重启服务">3. 重启服务&lt;/h3>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">systemctl restart shadowsocks-libev
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">systemctl status shadowsocks-libev
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="4-检查服务状态">4. 检查服务状态&lt;/h3>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1"># 检查端口监听&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">netstat -tlnp &lt;span class="p">|&lt;/span> grep &lt;span class="m">8388&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1"># 查看日志&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">journalctl -u shadowsocks-libev -n &lt;span class="m">50&lt;/span> --no-pager
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="5-检查防火墙">5. 检查防火墙&lt;/h3>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1"># 检查 UFW 状态&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">ufw status
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1"># 如果 UFW 启用，开放端口&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">ufw allow 8388/tcp
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="6-云服务商安全组">6. 云服务商安全组&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>重要！&lt;/strong> 必须在云服务商控制台开放 TCP 8388 端口。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>配置代理加速github访问</title><link>https://bluespace.eu.org/post/%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7/%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86%E5%8A%A0%E9%80%9Fgithub%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE/</link><pubDate>Sat, 28 Feb 2026 03:24:21 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://bluespace.eu.org/post/%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7/%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86%E5%8A%A0%E9%80%9Fgithub%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="nodejs-shadowsocks-完整配置指南">Node.js Shadowsocks 完整配置指南&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="架构说明">架构说明&lt;/h2>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">本地电脑 海外服务器
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">┌─────────────┐ ┌──────────────┐
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">│ 浏览器 │────SOCKS5────▶│ Shadowsocks │
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">│ (1080) │ │ Server │
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">│ │ │ │
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">│ Node.js │────加密──────▶│ (ss-server) │
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">│ 客户端 │ │ │
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">└─────────────┘ └──────────────┘
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> │ │
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> └─────────────访问 GitHub ─────┘
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;hr>
&lt;h2 id="第一部分服务端配置海外服务器">第一部分：服务端配置（海外服务器）&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 id="11-安装-shadowsocks-服务端">1.1 安装 Shadowsocks 服务端&lt;/h3>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1"># SSH 连接到服务器&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">ssh root@your-server-ip
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1"># 更新包管理器&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">apt update
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1"># 安装 shadowsocks-libev&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">apt install shadowsocks-libev -y
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="12-创建配置文件">1.2 创建配置文件&lt;/h3>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">cat &amp;gt; /etc/shadowsocks-libev/config.json &lt;span class="s">&amp;lt;&amp;lt; EOF
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s">{
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s"> &amp;#34;server&amp;#34;: &amp;#34;xxx.xxx.xxx.xxx&amp;#34;,
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s"> &amp;#34;server_port&amp;#34;: 8388,
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s"> &amp;#34;password&amp;#34;: &amp;#34;YourStrongPassword123!&amp;#34;,
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s"> &amp;#34;timeout&amp;#34;: 300,
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s"> &amp;#34;method&amp;#34;: &amp;#34;aes-256-gcm&amp;#34;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s">}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="s">EOF&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;strong>配置说明&lt;/strong>：&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>ssh连接服务器踩坑点</title><link>https://bluespace.eu.org/post/%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7/%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5/ssh%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E8%B8%A9%E5%9D%91%E7%82%B9/</link><pubDate>Wed, 25 Feb 2026 21:36:52 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://bluespace.eu.org/post/%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7/%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5/ssh%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E8%B8%A9%E5%9D%91%E7%82%B9/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="通过密钥连接服务器踩坑配置正确但是连接失败">通过密钥连接服务器踩坑——配置正确但是连接失败&lt;/h1>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>初始状态&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>已成功生成SSH密钥对（ed25519）&lt;/li>
&lt;li>已将公钥添加到服务器的 ~/.ssh/authorized_keys - 权限设置正确（.ssh 目录700，authorized_keys 文件600）&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;ol start="2">
&lt;li>问题表现
ssh -o BatchMode=yes -o PasswordAuthentication=no &lt;a href="mailto:username@ip">username@ip&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;h2 id="结果permission-denied-password">结果：Permission denied (password)&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>即使公钥已在服务器上，公钥认证仍然失败。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>机顶盒刷机linux系统</title><link>https://bluespace.eu.org/post/%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7/%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5/%E6%9C%BA%E9%A1%B6%E7%9B%92%E5%88%B7%E6%9C%BAlinux%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F/</link><pubDate>Wed, 25 Feb 2026 10:41:06 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://bluespace.eu.org/post/%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7/%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5/%E6%9C%BA%E9%A1%B6%E7%9B%92%E5%88%B7%E6%9C%BAlinux%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="h96max-rk3318-464g的刷机教程">H96Max rk3318 4+64G的刷机教程&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>相信很多朋友已经搜索了一大堆这个机型的刷机教程，再此之前我也搜索过，不过对我的帮助不大，所以我又连续几天在armbian官方论坛搜索查询、向大神请教。最终解决了刷机难题。 首先，我们来确认一下机型吧，看看图片和型号是否对得上。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>terminus</title><link>https://bluespace.eu.org/post/%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7/%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5/terminus/</link><pubDate>Sun, 22 Feb 2026 09:55:15 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://bluespace.eu.org/post/%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7/%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5/terminus/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="terminus快捷键使用合集">terminus快捷键使用合集&lt;/h2>
